   139                                  ;
   140                                  ;       Hardware-Defined Values
   141                                  ;
   142                                  ;       EKEYB...        8042 or "PS/2 Controller" (Keyboard Controller) values
   143                                  ;
   144                                  ;       Firmware-Defined Values
   145                                  ;
   146                                  ;       EBIOS...        Basic Input/Output System (BIOS) values
   147                                  ;
   148                                  ;       Operating System Values
